=Analyze these RMIS industry news items focusing on {{ $json.formData?.focusArea || 'general trends' }}:

Title: {{ $json.title }}
Description: {{ $json.description }}
Specific Focus: {{ $json.formData?.specificTopic || 'industry developments' }}

Based on this news and the focus area of {{ $json.formData?.focusArea || 'RMIS industry' }}, provide:

1. Key trends affecting {{ $json.formData?.focusArea || 'the industry' }}
2. Strategic implications for risk managers and CROs
3. Opportunities for thought leadership content
4. Potential blog angles and LinkedIn post concepts
5. Current challenges in {{ $json.formData?.focusArea || 'risk management' }}

Provide a comprehensive strategic analysis in 300 words that will inform content creation.

